com.nimbusds.openid.connect.claims
Class AddressClaims

java.lang.Object
  com.nimbusds.openid.connect.claims.JSONObjectClaims
      com.nimbusds.openid.connect.claims.AddressClaims
All Implemented Interfaces:
Claim<net.minidev.json.JSONObject>
public class AddressClaims
extends JSONObjectClaims
implements Claim<net.minidev.json.JSONObject>

UserInfo address claims, serialisable to a JSON object.

Example UserInfo address claims set: 

 {
   "user_id"     : "248289761001",
   "name"        : "Jane Doe",
   "given_name"  : "Jane",
   "family_name" : "Doe",
   "email"       : "janedoe@example.com",
   "picture"     : "http://example.com/janedoe/me.jpg"
 }

See http://openid.net/specs/openid-connect-messages-1_0.html#address_claim

Version:
0.9 (2012-05-17)
Author:
Vladimir Dzhuvinov
